== 名下馬匹  ==
梁柏濤、梁智焙父子是[[香港賽馬會|香港賽馬會]]會員，他亦有在香港養馬，名下賽駒多數以「正本」起名，包括「正本仁心(J330)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/OtherHorse.asp?HorseNo=J330 |title=香港賽馬會-正本仁心 |accessdate=2013-01-07 |archive-date=2014-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105164240/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/OtherHorse.asp?HorseNo=J330 |dead-url=no }}</ref>」、「正本大師(L005)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/OtherHorse.asp?HorseNo=L005 |title=香港賽馬會-正本大師 |accessdate=2013-01-07 |archive-date=2014-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105164516/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/OtherHorse.asp?HorseNo=L005 |dead-url=no }}</ref>」、「仁心仁術(M332)<ref>[http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/OtherHorse.asp?HorseNo=M332 香港賽馬會-仁心仁術]</ref>」、「海南花梨(M378)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/OtherHorse.asp?HorseNo=M378 |title=香港賽馬會-海南花梨 |accessdate=2016-04-20 |archive-date=2016-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420105504/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/OtherHorse.asp?HorseNo=M378 |dead-url=no }}</ref>」、「健康真知(P219)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/Horse.asp?HorseNo=P219 |title=香港賽馬會-健康真知 |accessdate=2013-08-26 |archive-date=2013-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130619032523/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/horse.asp?horseno=P219 |dead-url=no }}</ref>」和「正本雄心(V303)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/Horse.asp?HorseNo=V303 |title=香港賽馬會-正本雄心 |accessdate=2016-04-20 |archive-date=2016-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160429191530/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/horse.asp?horseno=V303 |dead-url=no }}</ref>」、「正本開心」、「盛唐文心」、「正本歡心」。

而旗下馬匹「正本仁心(J330)」在港出賽二十次，更取得四場頭馬，成績彪炳，直至2011-2012馬季宣布退役。

